{"type": "article", "id": 17106, "title": "带把手的餐具", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-05T10:11:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 50, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606003409eanYyvbQtElFpRJz.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t继不久前推出可叠在一起的拖鞋后，nendo 又为个人品牌 by | n 推出了这些带把手的餐具，包括圆形的碗和盘子，每样都有三种尺寸。这些把手不仅为了方便悬挂放置，还可能改变用餐习惯，颠覆传统扣着碗底的使用方式。当热菜刚盛到碗里时，一个带把手的盘子或碗也许能方便传送，至少增加了安全感。不同型号的碗和盘子都配有 5 种颜色，它们相互之间都可以搭配。<a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/en/works/totte-plate-2/?erelease\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144253cxQwgyCWjI1bf2r7.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144254FoQh3P0uEr9WmLxi.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144254gtUVcHslOijaAxBY.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261442549v5LhQxBHO18Yoag.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144255HAoDUBYyjSuFEbMG.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}